<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-47-0841 </DOCNO><TEXT>Beginning with an up-date on research and development activities in thefield of solar energy conversion, this paper then discusses the expectedincreased growth in the number of solar thermal energy installations.Data are provided to show the rapidly falling costs of the installations.Marketing projections are made to the year 2000. Flowsheets are usedto illustrate some of the more efficient installations in operation.</TEXT></DOC>